  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-special\">black-market modification</span> for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Movement Systems</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">jetpack tank capacity</span>, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">jetpack fuel efficiency</span>and Exosuit <span class=\"name name-stellar\">speed boost duration</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一项<span class=\"name name-special\">黑市改装</span>，适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装运动系统</span>。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块功能灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">喷气背包燃料容量</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">喷气背包燃料效率</span>和套装<span class=\"name name-stellar\">速度提升持续时间</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">強化套裝移動系統</span>的<span class=\"name name-special\">黑市改造</span>。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能改善的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">噴射背包儲槽容量</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">噴射背包燃料效率</span>和強化套裝<span class=\"name name-stellar\">加速持續時間</span>。"
